<http://dx.doi.org/10.17161/jom.v0i64.5775>
    bibo:endPage "11" ;
    bibo:issue "64" ;
    bibo:journal "Journal of Melitology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2016-12-02" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2016" ;
    dc:creator "Packer, Laurence" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Epeolini from northern Chile, with the first record of Triepeolus for the country and a key to Chilean species of Doeringiella (Hymenoptera: Apidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8057319>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8057321> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8057319>
    dc:description "Figures 1–3. Triepeolus cecilyae, new species, holotype male. 1. Lateral habitus. 2. Dorsal view of metasoma to show complete hair band on T3. 3. Metasomal sterna to show pale setae covering S3. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8057319/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8057321>
    dc:description "Figures 4–6. Triepeolus cecilyae, new species, holotype male. 4. Forewing to show relative lengths of submarginal cells. 5. Metasomal S7 and S8. 6. Genital capsule. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8057321/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

